<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Classic Burger Recipe</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Classic Burger Recipe</h1>

    <p>
        This classic burger recipe is easy to make and perfect for lunch or dinner.
        It features a juicy beef patty, fresh vegetables, and a soft burger bun.
    </p>

    <img
        src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/recipe.jpg"
        alt="A delicious homemade burger"
    >

    <h2>Ingredients</h2>

    <ul>
        <li>1 burger bun</li>
        <li>150g ground beef</li>
        <li>1 slice cheddar cheese</li>
        <li>Lettuce leaves</li>
        <li>Tomato slices</li>
        <li>1 tablespoon ketchup</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Instructions</h2>

    <ol>
        <li>Season the ground beef and shape it into a patty.</li>
        <li>Cook the patty on a hot grill or pan until fully cooked.</li>
        <li>Place the cheese on top of the patty and let it melt.</li>
        <li>Toast the burger bun lightly.</li>
        <li>Add lettuce, tomato, and the cooked patty to the bun.</li>
        <li>Spread ketchup and serve immediately.</li>
    </ol>

</body>
</html>
